{"tid":800354,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有得揀，你會揀 普通樣有父幹 vs 靚到癲 普通身家？","createTime":"2018-08-30T19:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T22:02:52.000Z","uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a83d301f4d73ad014b2aa9bb8a727cf7f06286cf","tid":800354,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:46:42.000Z","msg":"我諗我會揀靚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做靚人嘅感受遠爽於有錢 <br />\n拎到一身名牌都唔及你簡單著件T-shirt <br />\n你就是移動名牌嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且全世界都會對你好好 連侍應都特別好服務"},{"pid":"88012d9be3ae9e68e7747fcd340552fa58d9cef6","tid":800354,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:49:08.000Z","msg":"不是投票post 純粹討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且童年時期大家未明有冇錢嘅時候<br />\n都係靚嘅小朋友受盡萬千寵愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 受同學歡迎<br />\n唔靚就算幾有錢都係冇咗個快樂童年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac7e32e9f2a59995b097c6499225e05b66791d5","tid":800354,"uid":129189,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:50:53.000Z","msg":"男-普通樣父幹<br />\n女-靚到癲普通身家"},{"pid":"7fced231415d543324dcffdb02a4fe75f4e53ce6","tid":800354,"uid":108266,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3ac7e32e9f2a59995b097c6499225e05b66791d5","tid":800354,"uid":129189,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:50:53.000Z","msg":"男-普通樣父幹<br />\n女-靚到癲普通身家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"有錢屌盡世間西，有樣吸盡世界財"},{"pid":"bbdaca40e24e03ad272a90ab9797cc509479